程序包 org.giiwa.conf

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Config
    The Class Config is whole configuration of system, usually is a copy of "giiwa.properties"
    Global
    The Class Global is extended of Config, it can be "overrided" by module or configured, it stored in database
    Local
